---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div
    class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[300px]"
>
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-[20rem] h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div
            id="dough-visual"
            class="rounded-full bg-[#f3e5ab] shadow-inner transition-all duration-500 relative z-10"
        >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-white/40 to-black/5">
            </div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-4 flex flex-col items-center opacity-30 pointer-events-none z-0"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:hand-back-right" class="w-24 h-24 text-slate-400" />
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold">Ref.</span>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">
            Ø <span id="visual-diameter">30</span>cm aprox.
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-slate-500 text-sm max-w-xs mx-auto">
        El tamaño visual representa el diámetro aproximado de la pizza estirada según el peso de la
        bola.
    </p>
</div>
